{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harborde blends roguelike combat with settlement management. Each run feels new with procedural events and achievements that reward resources, skills, and upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your settlement is your base, where you can farm, fish, craft, and build. Use a modular system to expand with workshops, fishing docks, or farms, and automate tasks by hiring NPCs to gather resources and craft items. Customize and grow your settlement to prepare for the challenges ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396310/extras/ezgif-6-d7fed51a22__Optimized_.gif?t=1737318284\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Combat</strong>: Fast paced action with unpredictable procedural events.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Settlement Building</strong>: Create and expand your base with modular structures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Crafting &amp; Upgrades</strong>: Forge weapons, tools, and gear to boost your runs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Farming &amp; Fishing</strong>: Grow crops and fish and gather resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Automated Systems</strong>: Hire NPCs to handle tasks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Achievements &amp; Rewards</strong>: Unlock skills, resources, and upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Endless Replayability</strong>: Procedural levels and dynamic events make every run unique.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Community</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396310/extras/Discord.png?t=1737318284\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our Discord community for feedback, suggestions, playtesting, and more! Ask anythi